{
  "chapter": 33,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲和徐子陵在东溟号上养伤，讨论与单琬晶的纠葛。丑婢和如茵先后来访，如茵对两人与巴陵帮的关系大为不满。晚宴上，东溟夫人款待众人，尚明谈及突厥入侵中原的危局，尚公看出寇徐二人武功不凡。两人计划趁东溟夫人会见李世民时偷取账簿，却被单琬晶召见，她提议让李阀保护二人，被拒绝后愤然离去。两人潜入书房搜寻账簿未果，尚公现身擒住他们，正要动手时黑衣人突然袭击尚公抢走账簿。寇徐趁乱逃入湖中，反将黑衣人打伤夺回账簿，游向李世民的大船。李秀宁收留二人，李世民赶到，感谢他们完成任务，承诺李家得天下后必不薄待。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "真的没事吗？那雌儿真辣手，只不过没兴趣和她兜搭吧了！竟认作是甚么仇仇怨怨的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "细声点好吗？给她偷听到就麻烦了。嘿！告诉你一件奇事，当时我体内真气发动，竟一下子好了很多，假若能再早点运气，说不定可轻易挡她那一掌呢。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不过这一掌都算物有所值，只要死不了就行啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "莫要看她凶兮兮的，事实上她却是不自觉地爱上了你，只是因自己身有所属，你又当她不是东西，急怒攻心下，才出手伤了你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "去你娘的爱上我，这种爱不要也罢。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "虽然你曾骂她勾三搭四，没有羞耻心，开罪她来得比我严重，但我对她亦好不了多少，而她偏只是找上了你来泄愤，这种女儿家心事最是微妙。你去见她时，那小子尚明坐立不安，神情都不知多么精采。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这么说那尚明该就是恶婆娘公主的未过门夫婿了，唉！就算整个东溟派的人跪在身前我也不会入派，男人变成了娘儿有甚么瘾头。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "最大的瘾头就是由女人来养我们。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "今晚到了微山湖后，东溟夫人和那恶婆娘公主会去见李世民的老爹，那就是我们下手偷东西的时候了，从这里攀窗下去，只是举手之劳吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_bi",
      "speaker_name": "丑婢",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "还痛吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_chou_bi",
      "text": "想来休息两天便没事了，多谢姐姐关心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_bi",
      "speaker_name": "丑婢",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "谁关心你，只是夫人今晚想和你们吃饭，教我来看你们的情况吧！既没甚么事就成了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yin",
      "speaker_name": "如茵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可以进来吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ru_yin",
      "text": "好姐姐请进！",
      "tone": "热情",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yin",
      "speaker_name": "如茵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "夫人说得不错，表面看来你虽伤得厉害，其实并不严重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_ru_yin",
      "text": "只是尚有点疼痛吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yin",
      "speaker_name": "如茵",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你的内功真怪，虚虚荡荡的，教人难知深浅。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ru_yin",
      "text": "就叫莫测高深了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yin",
      "speaker_name": "如茵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你正经点好吗？说真的，我对你们的印象并不比公主好多少。竟与巴陵帮那些丧尽天良的人鬼混，想学他们般贩卖人口吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ru_yin",
      "text": "我们不知那香玉山是巴陵帮的人嘛！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yin",
      "speaker_name": "如茵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那为何又要到他们开的赌场去？不要说你们不知那是赌场吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ru_yin",
      "text": "我们确不知那是间赌馆，还以为是所妓院。",
      "tone": "尴尬",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yin",
      "speaker_name": "如茵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ru_yin",
      "text": "姐姐你怎知我们当时的处境，走投无路下，只好找个地方躲起来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yin",
      "speaker_name": "如茵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这只是借口，你们想到那种低三下四的地方鬼混才真。看你两人好眉好貌，底下里却坏成这样子，看我以后睬不睬你们。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yin",
      "speaker_name": "如茵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你的臭手敢碰我？公主说得对，这世上的男人没多少个是好人来的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ru_yin",
      "speaker_name": "如茵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我很少这样动气的，都是你们不好！这样吧，若肯答应我以后不到那种地方去，我就原谅你们！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ru_yin",
      "text": "那我们岂非要改行修练童子功。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "幸好没给你抢先答应，否则以后做人还有哈乐趣。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "又开罪多一个人了。现在船上我们除东溟夫人外，可说举目无亲。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这条船载的都是怪人，幸好我们快要走了，否则迟早成了他们一伙。琉球还是不去也罢，肯定半个耍乐的地方都没有。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "耍甚么乐，每趟要到青楼去都是头头碰着黑，看来我们两条命都欠了青楼运。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我才不信邪，来！我们先练我们的绝世神功，只要能耳听八方，就可进行大计了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最令人忧虑是突厥人的动向，现在鹰扬派的梁师都和刘武周都投向了他，分别被封为大度毗伽可汗和定扬可汗，这两个叛贼还是奉突厥可汗之命进迫太原，若李渊守不住太原，突厥入必会乘机进侵，那时中原危矣。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "单燕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李阀现在是腹背受敌，独孤阀和宇文阀都恨不得他们全军覆没。但此事谁都帮不上忙，只好看李阀的造化了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_yu_die",
      "speaker_name": "单玉蝶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好李渊有几个好儿子，而太原位于汾水上游，在太行山和黄河之间，控山带河、踞天下之肩背，为河东之根本，兵精粮足。加上李渊父子广施恩德，结纳豪杰，势力正不住扩展，非是没有一战之力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不过李渊乃是优柔寡断之辈，终日念着自己是那昏君的姨表兄弟，也终有一天会给那昏君累死。若我是李渊，趁现在昏君把关中军队调往江都一带镇压杜伏威，而瓦岗军更牵制了隋军在洛阳的主力，就索性攻入京师，起兵作反了。",
      "tone": "不满",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "单青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜我们受祖规所限，不能插手中原的事，否则见到世民时，就可向他痛陈利害了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_ming_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "东溟夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们看得到的事，难道别人想不到吗？这事再不必谈论。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_gong",
      "speaker_name": "尚公",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们的功夫是谁教的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_gong",
      "text": "是娘教的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_ming_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "东溟夫人",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "谁是你的娘？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_dong_ming_fu_ren",
      "text": "他的娘就是我的娘，别人都唤她作罗刹女。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_ming_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "东溟夫人",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "罗刹女傅君绰有名心狠手辣，想不到不但收了你们作义子，更为你们牺牲了性命，也算异数了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_gong",
      "speaker_name": "尚公",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不对！你们的功夫练了多久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_gong",
      "text": "超过一年了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_gong",
      "speaker_name": "尚公",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "假若你们能避过走火入魔之厄，将来该可有一番作为。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_ming_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "东溟夫人",
      "listener": "char_shang_gong",
      "text": "美仙曾察看过他们的行气法门，却是茫无头绪，不知从何入手，这才打消收他们入派传功之念。尚公若有办法，何不指点他们两手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这世上太多恩将仇报的人，你看那尚明，狗仗主人威，对我们摆出一副高高在上的不屑神态。哈！幸好本少心胸广阔，不会和他计较。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若真不计较，就提也不该提了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "说得对！由这刻开始，我们再不说这家伙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "怎样才知夫人她们几时离船去见李小子呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "还不简单吗？船停的时候，就是她们离船的时候了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "假若夫人约了李小子到船上来见面，我们岂非好梦成空？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不理得这么多了，只要她们集中到上面的大厅去，我们立即动手偷东西，李小子和他老爹的命运，就在我们的手上了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不是说过宇文阀的人想偷袭东溟号吗？为何全不见踪影呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你问我？那我去问谁？咦！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那是尚公的声音，化了灰都可认出来。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这老家伙的叹息声为何会这么大声呢？就像在我们耳旁叹气的样子。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不理得这么多了，我们在半炷香后，就攀窗下去偷东西，然后再借水遁。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_bi",
      "speaker_name": "丑婢",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "快出来！公主要见你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_bi",
      "speaker_name": "丑婢",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "进去吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "speaker_name": "单琬晶",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那天我心情不大好，一时错手伤了徐公子，现在算我道歉好了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "speaker_name": "单琬晶",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们为何不说话。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "text": "我们有甚么好说的，你要说就尽避说个够吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "speaker_name": "单琬晶",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我对你们确不算好，但这是由你们一手造成的，但幸好这一切立即会结柬了，我巳为你们安排了去处。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "speaker_name": "单琬晶",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "莫要大惊小怪，现在江湖上有能力保护你们的人数不出多少个来。李阀却是其中之一，凭我们和李阀的关系，只要我们肯开口，他们自然会照顾你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "text": "有劳公主费心了，我们这种人自在惯了，最怕寄人篱下，看别人脸色做人，公主若看我们不顺眼，我们便立即跳湖溜之，如此皆大欢喜，两家高兴。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "speaker_name": "单琬晶",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你在说甚么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "text": "仲少说得这么口齿伶利，公主竟会听不清楚吗？我们绝不会去求人收留可怜，更不用受你这种所谓的恩惠，现在我们就回房收拾东西，自行离去，请了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "speaker_name": "单琬晶",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "给我站着！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "speaker_name": "单琬晶",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这样好吗？我们只请李阀的人送你们一程，到了安全的地方后，便任你们离去。你们或者仍不知道，那昏君巳下了严令，怎样都要由你们身上把《长生诀》追回来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "text": "若是如此，我们更不可登上李阀的大船，说到底李阀都是皇帝小儿其中一只走狗，怎知会不会见利忘义，出卖我两兄弟。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "speaker_name": "单琬晶",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不要把人看眨了，当你见到李世民时，才会明白甚么才是真正使人心悦诚服的英雄人物，勿要过虑了，我可以东溟派之名，保证不会发生这种事。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "text": "理得他是真英雄还是假英雄，我们自由自在惯了，故没有兴趣去攀附公主心中看得起的英雄人物。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "text": "公主这提议，恐怕并未得到夫人的同意吧！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_wan_jing",
      "speaker_name": "单琬晶",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "给我滚，待会回来时，不要再给我见到你们，你们要去送死，就去死好了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那婆娘定是把那本东西带了去和李小子算账，今趟完了，最苦是我们须立即离去，否则就要给恶婆娘废物般丢往水里去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "要走就趁早走吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_gong",
      "speaker_name": "尚公",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们耍找这本账簿吗？有本事就来拿吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_gong",
      "speaker_name": "尚公",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "夫人将保安之责，交给我这老头，老夫自然不会令她失望。这些天来老夫一直留意你们，听你们的说话，更曾作出警告，可是你们仍是贼性难改，令老夫非常失望。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_gong",
      "text": "我们是受朋友所托……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_gong",
      "speaker_name": "尚公",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "老夫那理得你们是为了甚么理由，只知这账簿关系到我们东溟派的信誉。不过若非给你两人一闹，我们也不知道这么一本账簿，竟是祸乱的根源。夫人回来时，老夫会请夫人把它毁了，免得再被人利用来作为斗争的工具。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_gong",
      "speaker_name": "尚公",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们的本质还不算坏，未失天真，有时我听你们说话时，自己也忍不住笑起来呢。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_gong",
      "text": "尚公可否放我兄弟两人一马呢？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_gong",
      "speaker_name": "尚公",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "公还公，私还私，我东溟派最重法规，我尚平一生从没有半步行差踏错，怎能为你两个小子晚节不保。但夫人回来后，我却可为你们说两句好话。现在给老夫跪下。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_gong",
      "speaker_name": "尚公",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若这是换了十年之后，老夫真不敢包保自己这副老骨头能否捱得起你两人联手一击，但现在你们的斤两差太远了，来吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知死活的家伙。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 517
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "希望李小子的人不要当我们是贼就好了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 543,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "上去吧！罢才我差点给那老家伙震散了我的嫩骨头哩！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 545,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shan_mei",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 561,
      "line_end": 561
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_shan_mei",
      "text": "我叫寇仲，是李……",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 563,
      "line_end": 563
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shan_mei",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "还不快进来，给人看到就糟了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 565,
      "line_end": 565
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shan_mei",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "果然没错，你两人在这里待上一会，让我去看二哥回来了没有。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 575,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这妞儿真美，早知不要银两而要人就好了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 583,
      "line_end": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "今趟这个让给你，下次再遇上这种级数的甜妞儿，就是我的了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 585,
      "line_end": 585
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你的我的，也不想想我们是甚么束西，人家是千金小姐，生于高门大族，何时才轮得到我们？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 589,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "仲少何时变得这么谦虚了，你不是常说自己将来是武林高手吗？又说可封侯拜将，为甚么忽然这么泄气？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 593,
      "line_end": 595
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "说说就可以，我们的功夫比起刚才那失运的高手便差远了。他毫无防备下任我们打，亦只是吐那么鸟儿的一口血就算了。还有那姓尚的老家伙也说没个十年八年，我们的功夫都拿不出来见人。是了，待会记得问李小子再要两把刀，没了刀连打架都不成了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 603
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "千万不可，否则这一世我们也休想学懂拳脚功夫，没有刀便用手，一样可使出李大哥教的血战十式。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 607,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shan_mei",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "为甚么坐在地上？还不起来？",
      "tone": "嗔怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 613,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "成功了！适才东溟夫人还亲笔写了一封信，要我立即赶往太原交给爹。我李家将来如得天下，必不会薄待两位。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 617,
      "line_end": 621
    }
  ],
